Title: Os Crimes de Diogo Alves
Writer: João Freire Correia, Lino Ferreira, Barbosa Júnior
Actors: Alfredo de Sousa, Amélia Soares, Gertrudes Lima
Plot: Between 1836 and 1839, Diogo Alves, committed a series of crimes and murders, most of them taking place in the Aqueduto of Águas Livres, before being caught by the authorities and being hanged.
